---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>🧑‍🚀 Hello, AITAH!</h1>
			<p>
				Content

Our content is carefully crafted tO inform, entertain, and inspire. Each article is written with attention to detail, combining engaging narratives with useful information. Whether you’re looking for lifestyle advice, tech trends, travel experiences, or motivational stories, our blog provides a wealth of knowledge and perspectives.

Stories

We believe stories are the heart of every connection. Through real-life experiences, anecdotes, and creative storytelling, we bring our readers closer to ideas that matter. Our stories aim to inspire, educate, and spark meaningful conversations within our community.

Analytics

Behind every post, our analytics system tracks engagement, trends, and reader preferences. This allows us to understand what resonates with our audience, improve our content, and provide a tailored reading experience. We value your interaction and use insights to continually enhance our blog.

Homepage

Our homepage is designed to be a welcoming gateway. Featuring featured articles, trending stories, and easy navigation, it ensures that every visitor can find what they’re looking for quickly. With a clean layout, intuitive design, and rich visuals, the homepage sets the tone for an engaging reading journey.
			</p>
		
			
			
		
		</main>
		<Footer />
